reviewText:
Truly a visceral experience. This postmodern horror game deconstructs the genre, and elevates ones understanding of what it means to be human. The psychoanalysis of every character perfectly contextualises their inner feelings.

With my limited vocabulary, I find it hard to accurately portray the majesty of this game. I'll have to settle by ranking this behemoth of a game using a vacuous number scale;

10/10

Let me put it this way.

If I had to choose between sucking the ♥♥♥♥ out of honey boo boos mothers ♥♥♥♥ and playing this game again;

I would be puckered up.
